highlights.text: Henrique & Juliano has the most spots on Top Songs Brazil. “Última Saudade - Ao Vivo” is the highest at #11.
“Lapada Dela - Ao Vivo” by Grupo Menos É Mais and Matheus Fernandes has been on Top Songs Brazil the longest, at 882 days straight.
“Coisas Que Eu Sei” by Felipe Amorim is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Brazil, up 95 spots at #101.
